Class SLLNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • utilities.SLLNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class SLLNode
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A node to be used in a Single Linked List class. Contains an element (any Object), and a reference to the next SLLNode in the list.

    April 8th, 2017
